  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个TCP报文结构的示意图，用来给团队讲解协议栈。关键是用packet-beta格式，把各个字段的位宽和含义都标清楚。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "packet-beta",
        "TCP报文结构"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，packet-beta很适合这种位域展示。我先确认一下字段顺序——是从Source Port开始，然后是Destination Port，接着是Sequence Number和Acknowledgment Number，这样对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Source Port",
        "Destination Port",
        "Sequence Number",
        "Acknowledgment Number"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，前96位按标准顺序来。Data Offset和Reserved各占4位和6位，接下来是6个控制位——URG、ACK、PSH、RST、SYN、FIN，每个都是1位。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Data Offset",
        "Reserved",
        "URG",
        "ACK",
        "PSH",
        "RST",
        "SYN",
        "FIN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，控制位部分已加上。Window字段是16位对吧？然后Checksum和Urgent Pointer各16位，这样到160位为止。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Window",
        "Checksum",
        "Urgent Pointer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "最后两个字段需要特殊标注一下。Options部分我们实际用的是Infra_IngressController，Data部分对应Infra_LoadBalancer，这是为了和运维那边的术语对齐。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Options",
        "Data",
        "Infra_IngressController",
        "Infra_LoadBalancer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "收到，Options是32位（160-191），Data是64位（192-255）。我直接把括号里的标注写成\"Options (Infra_IngressController)\"和\"Data (Infra_LoadBalancer)\"可以吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Options",
        "Data",
        "Infra_IngressController",
        "Infra_LoadBalancer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "可以，这样标注很清晰。对了，图标题用\"Estructura del paquete TCP\"吧，这是给西班牙同事准备的版本。",
      "elements_involved": [
